Prerequisites
=============

GTK+ requires the following packages:

 - The GLib, Pango, GdkPixbuf, ATK and cairo libraries. STLWRT requires at least
   GLib 2.28.0, Pango 1.20, GdkPixbuf 2.21.0, ATK 1.29.2 and cairo 1.6.0.

 - gobject-introspection 0.9.3 or newer.


Installation procedure
======================

First change directory (cd) into the directory where you unpacked the STLWRT
sources:

  $ tar -xzf stlwrt-[version].tar.gz             # unpack the sources
  $ cd stlwrt-[version]			         # change to the toplevel directory
  $ ./configure				         # run the `configure' script
  $ make				         # build STLWRT
  [ Become root if necessary ]
  $ sudo make install			         # install STLWRT
